// November 16th
 - simplify the meaning of heat%(transition) = fraction (H to H), the rest produces elec (E to E or H to E)
  hence the formula in eTransferRatio is X (quantity) * (1 - r1) * (1 - heat%)
  heat% = 100 -> no impact, heat% -> 100% electrification -> gain is X * (1 - r1)

